  <para>
    Save a &mesh; to a file, together with its &skel;, &micro;, and
    all of its &materials;.  All information about &fields;,
    &equations;, and <link
    linkend='Section-Concepts-Mesh-BoundaryCondition'>boundary
    conditions</link> is saved as well.
  </para>
  <para>
    The <varname>format</varname> argument is one of the data file
    formats discussed in <xref
    linkend='Section-Concepts-FileFormats'/>.  The
    <varname>varname</varname> argument is the <link
    linkend="Section-Concepts-Path">path</link> to the &mesh; that is
    being saved.
  </para>

